text: Marin Bolocan (born 9 August 1937) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
